channel.title: Pbscape, Re-rising of Delta
channel.description:
[center] [img]http://i52.tinypic.com/1izkoi.png[/img]
[b]Info[/b]: Server Name: Pbscape Server based off of: Deltascape Owners: Pblord7.
[b]Goals[/b]: -Very stable server -Have a decent player average -Great Economy -Fun to play server -Very few glitches
[b]What's been fixed and added? (ALOT MORE THAN THIS)[/b]: [code] Colored Yell Colored Talk Fixing PVP timers Fixing Ice Barrage Make Slayer easier Spirit Shields Donator Island Angel Wings for Donators (use with ::fly) Colored Talk New Death Cape Void Mele Helm Void Range Helm Void Mage Helm Void Top Void Bottom Dragon Claws Spec Crossbow Emote AGS Spec BGS Spec ZGS Spec SGS Spec Overloads Rocktails Karil's Bow on NPC's Staff Of Light Magic in PVP/NPCS(while attacking) Fix magic (can cast on any levels) Dragon Bow Glitch Fix Overload Effect Black Mask (Works just like Rune scape and help's a lot during Slayer Tasks.) PVP Drops DFS Effect DDS Glitch Fix Bank Pins Prayer Curses X2 XP System for Double EXP Weekends You attack NPC's before they attack you Elemental Staff's don't use runes "Magic Staff" doesn't use runes Rocktail Effect Torva Effect (for when Torva is added) DDS Hits twice at the same time PKing Skill Kill Death Ratio Quick Chat for Skills Redid Slayer Anti-Leak for staff, Admins+ can not view Heriqun's shop so they can not leak Just coded NPC Hitting with dds (hitting both times) Heriqun now buys Spirit Beast head for 20M. New Clue Scrolls Spirit Shield Effects PVP Spirit Shield Effects PVM 99 PKing Store NPC Freezing DDoS, Flood, and SysiPKer Protection Buy X Perfect Grim Reaper on death, based off the one from Sinzscape, we just made it 100x better HP Glitch causing you not to die. Inferno Adze with randomly buring logs. Suggesting System Ring of Wealth
Range Dupe Food Dupe Bank Dupe Combat Dupe Drop Dupe Pvp Dupe Trade Dupe Cheat Client Dupe Trade Disconnect Dupe [/code]
[b]Media:[/b] Mage Following: [img]http://img683.imageshack.us/img683/9062/100magefollow.gif[/img] Mele Following: [img]http://img813.imageshack.us/img813/8854/100meleefollow.gif[/img] Range Following: [img]http://img15.imageshack.us/img15/780/100rangefollow.gif[/img] Spirit Shields: [img]http://img706.imageshack.us/img706/4129/allspiritshields.gif[/img] AGS Spec: [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/6xvtyu.gif[/img] BGS Spec: [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/j9ykx5.gif[/img] SGS Spec: [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/2555emb.gif[/img] ZGS Spec: [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/27y6gee.gif[/img] Saradomin Sword Spec: [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/ev0vgy.gif[/img] Dragon Claws Spec: [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/24osm68.gif[/img] Darkbow Spec: [img]http://i51.tinypic.com/4uhnwy.gif[/img] Anchor Spec: [img]http://www.gifninja.com/animatedgifs/85349/pbscape-anchor.gif[/img] Highscores: [img]http://screensnapr.com/e/oNt0Db.png[/img] Wilderness Obelisks: [IMG]http://i34.tinypic.com/214oxmf.jpg[/img] DDS Spec on NPCS: [img]http://i56.tinypic.com/fbfbra.png[/img] Astonishing godsword anims!
[img]http://i55.tinypic.com/2eowktk.gif[/img]
Earn your way to some new items!!
[img]http://screensnapr.com/e/NYghQ3.png[/img]
Fight bosses in newly added GWD maps!!
[img]http://i54.tinypic.com/2dr556h.png[/img]
New and old whip added, for the oldies, and for the new kids, choose which whip you like better!
[img]http://i53.tinypic.com/69fk8i.png[/img]
And also keeping the metal whips as well!
[img]http://i54.tinypic.com/xfqgdv.png[/img]
[img]http://screensnapr.com/e/5sQdLz.png[/img] This is all I have atm :D, please stay tune for more information! Atm there is no info on how you will get some of the newer items yet, but there will be!
[b]Spots open[/b]: Gfx designer: 0/1 Beta tester: 0/3 Server Developer: 2/3 Me, Youriduck Ingame Staff: Post information on the thread if applying for.
How to apply for different positons:

[b]My MSN: pblord7@sinzscape.net[/b] [b]Forums: http://pbscape.net[/b] [b]Youtube: BrokenRiver1[/b] [img]http://i53.tinypic.com/msg5xx.jpg[/img]
